{"name":"Knick","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Andradoran","alignment":"LE","hitDice":"7","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"27 (5d8 + 5)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"12","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"14","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 1 villain action, choosing from the options below. Only one Villain action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent villain actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the spy can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the spy can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The spy can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the spy's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the spy's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the spy dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Sneak Attack (1/Turn)","desc":"[MON] deals an extra [3d6] damage when he hits a target with a weapon attack and has advantage on the attack roll, or when the target is within 5 ft. of an ally that isn't incapacitated, and [MON] doesn't have disadvantage on the attack roll."}],"actions":[{"name":"Poisoned Dagger","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1d4] piercing damage and the target must make a DC 14 Constitution save or fall unconscious for a minute."},{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] slashing damage."},{"name":"Hand Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 30/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Cunning Action","desc":"On each of its turns, [MON] can use a bonus action to take the Dash, Disengage, or Hide action."},{"name":"Health Pot (3 total)","desc":"[MON] drinks a health potion or administers it to Rhedda. The health potion heals [2d4+2]."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Uncanny Dodge (1/day)","desc":"When [MON] is hit with an attack roll he can use his reaction to halve the damage."}],"legendaries":[{"name":"Drop Net (1/day)","desc":"[MON] makes a crossbow attack against the hidden net above the door (AC 10). On a success all creatures within a 15ftsquare within the door must make a DC [DEX SAVE] dexterity saving through or be restrained. A surprised creature has disadvantage on this save. A restrained creature, or ally, can make a DC [DEX SAVE] athletics or acrobatics check to free a creature."},{"name":"Flank","desc":"[MON] makes a weapon attack against a target adjacent to Rhedda or an echo. Rhedda may then use her reaction to swap places with any manifested echo."},{"name":"Smokescreen","desc":"[MON] throws a smoke bomb at a point within 30ft. A 20ft circle around that point becomes heavily obscured for a minute or until dispersed."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"int","order":3}],"skills":[{"name":"acrobatics","stat":"dex"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Thieve's Cant","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}